<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8212221>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. a, b, c. Humidicutis pindorama (JS485). a. basidiospores, b. basidia, c. lamellar trama hyphae. d, e, f. Neohygrocybe fumosa (JS600). d. basidiospores, e. basidia, f. cheilocystidia. Scale = 10 μm. Drawings by: J. S. Cardoso" ;
